high_descs: Walk over to where the head of lettuce is on the counter to the left of the microwave.
Pick up the head of lettuce off of the counter.
Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the head of lettuce inside on a shelf, then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and remove the head of lettuce then close the door.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left and walk over to the counter.
Put the chilled head of lettuce on the left edge of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right then turn left then right and head to the kitchen counter
PIck up the lettuce from the counter
Turn right and go to the fridge and turn left
Put the lettuce in the fridge and wait a bit, then take the lettuce out of the fridge
Turn left and head to the sink then turn left and head to the counter across from the sink
Put the lettuce on top of the spatula that is on the counter
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on a spatula on the counter

high_descs: Go forward, turn right, go forward to the lettuce to the left of the microwave.
Take the lettuce from the counter.
Turn right, go forward to the wall, turn left to the fridge.
Put the lettuce in the middle rack of the fridge to the right of the potato. Close then open the fridge. Take the lettuce from the fridge.
Turn left, go forward, at the sink turn left, go forward to the counter with the toaster.
Put the lettuce on the spatula near the left edge of the end of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold lettuce head on a counter.
